Module lanej.inventorysystem

Package lanej.inventorysystem

package lanej.inventorysystem
Contains the classes and interfaces related to managing inventory for a business. The package includes classes for managing products and parts, as well as interfaces for implementing inventory management methods.

The `Controller` package contains the controllers for the JavaFX views, which allow users to interact with and modify the inventory data.

The 'Model' package contains the classes that are primarily used to abstract the creation and deletion of inventory data.

The InventoryApplication class houses the main method, and ties all the classes in the Controller package together to make a cohesive application.
